{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a premium full-width Shopify section called "Dynamic SEO Content".
    
    This section will be reused across hundreds of service pages.
    
    The section must automatically organize content pulled from Shopify page metafields and generate a modern, highly readable layout without requiring manual editing.
    
    GOALS
    
    • Increase SEO relevance
    • Improve user experience
    • Improve readability
    • Help AI search engines understand page structure
    • Mobile-first design
    • Extremely clean typography
    • Fast loading
    • Fully responsive
    
    -----------------------------------
    CONTENT SOURCE
    -----------------------------------
    
    Automatically use:
    
    - page.title
    - page.content
    - page.metafields
    - Rich Text fields
    - Dynamic Headings
    - Dynamic Lists
    - Dynamic FAQ references
    
    Never hardcode content.
    
    Everything should populate automatically.
    
    -----------------------------------
    AUTO TABLE OF CONTENTS
    -----------------------------------
    
    Automatically scan the page content.
    
    Generate a floating modern Table of Contents.
    
    Include every H2
    Include every H3
    
    Clicking an item smoothly scrolls to that section.
    
    Highlight the active section while scrolling.
    
    Desktop:
    Sticky sidebar
    
    Mobile:
    Collapsible accordion
    
    Hide automatically if fewer than 3 headings exist.
    
    -----------------------------------
    AUTO CONTENT STYLING
    -----------------------------------
    
    Instead of displaying plain Shopify content, automatically redesign every section.
    
    Every H2 should become a premium heading.
    
    Large typography
    
    Bold
    
    Elegant spacing
    
    Animated underline
    
    Accent colour
    
    Every H3
    
    Medium weight
    
    Smaller underline
    
    Elegant spacing
    
    Paragraphs
    
    Maximum reading width
    
    Large line height
    
    Comfortable spacing
    
    Never allow huge blocks of text.
    
    Automatically split long content into readable sections.
    
    -----------------------------------
    TEXT HIGHLIGHTER
    -----------------------------------
    
    Automatically highlight important content.
    
    Examples:
    
    Important
    
    Professional
    
    Same Day
    
    Furniture Delivery
    
    Removalists
    
    Marketplace Pickup
    
    Affordable
    
    Fast
    
    Oversized Van
    
    Sydney
    
    Insured
    
    Experienced
    
    Heavy Items
    
    Fragile Items
    
    Book Today
    
    Free Quote
    
    Use elegant highlight styles.
    
    Examples:
    
    black text
    red underline
    
    soft red background
    
    marker highlight effect
    
    Do NOT overuse highlighting.
    
    -----------------------------------
    AUTO FEATURE BLOCKS
    -----------------------------------
    
    Detect lists automatically.
    
    Convert lists into modern cards.
    
    Example
    
    ✓ Same Day Delivery
    
    ✓ Professional Equipment
    
    ✓ Fully Insured
    
    ✓ Marketplace Pickup
    
    ✓ Apartment Moves
    
    ✓ Small Moves
    
    Each card uses:
    
    SVG icon
    
    Rounded corners
    
    Hover effect
    
    -----------------------------------
    AUTO CALLOUT BOXES
    -----------------------------------
    
    Detect important paragraphs.
    
    Convert them into premium callout cards.
    
    Examples:
    
    Pro Tip
    
    Important Information
    
    Need to Know
    
    Why Choose Us
    
    Helpful Advice
    
    -----------------------------------
    SEO STRUCTURE
    -----------------------------------
    
    Follow Google's preferred structure.
    
    H1
    
    Introduction
    
    H2
    
    H3
    
    Supporting paragraphs
    
    Lists
    
    FAQs
    
    Internal links
    
    Call to Action
    
    Semantic HTML only.
    
    Never skip heading hierarchy.
    
    -----------------------------------
    READABILITY
    -----------------------------------
    
    Automatically improve readability.
    
    Limit paragraph width.
    
    Increase white space.
    
    Improve typography hierarchy.
    
    Never allow walls of text.
    
    -----------------------------------
    DESIGN
    -----------------------------------
    
    Modern SaaS style.
    
    Minimal.
    
    Professional.
    
    Luxury service business.
    
    Colour palette
    
    Black
    
    White
    
    Red accent
    
    Rounded corners
    
    Subtle shadows
    
    Glassmorphism where appropriate
    
    Large spacing
    
    Beautiful typography
    
    Premium animations
    
    Smooth scrolling
    
    Fade-in animations
    
    Underline animations
    
    -----------------------------------
    RESPONSIVE
    -----------------------------------
    
    Perfect on:
    
    Desktop
    
    Tablet
    
    Mobile
    
    Large touch targets
    
    No horizontal scrolling
    
    -----------------------------------
    PERFORMANCE
    -----------------------------------
    
    Lazy load everything possible.
    
    No unnecessary JavaScript.
    
    Optimized CSS.
    
    SEO friendly.
    
    Accessibility compliant.
    
