    DYNAMIC PAGE DATA
    ────────────────────────
    
    Use available Shopify page data throughout the section:
    
    • page.title
    • page.handle
    • page.content
    • page.url
    • shop.name
    • service name metafield
    • suburb name metafield
    • service description metafield
    • service benefits metafield
    • areas served metafield
    • related services metafield
    • customer questions metafield
    • call-to-action metafield
    • internal links metafield
    
    Automatically hide individual content elements when their source data is empty.
    
    ────────────────────────
    DYNAMIC SEO INTRODUCTION
    ────────────────────────
    
    Create a short introductory content block above the main page content.
    
    Build the introduction using the available page title, service name, suburb name and service description metafields.
    
    Use a natural service-focused heading pattern such as:
    
    [Service Name] in [Suburb Name]
    
    Professional [Service Name] for [Suburb Name] Customers
    
    Reliable [Service Name] Across [Suburb Name]
    
    Local [Service Name] Available in [Suburb Name]
    
    Use page.title as the fallback heading source.
    
    Present the introduction as useful information for visitors, explaining:
    
    • What the service is
    • Who the service helps
    • Where the service is available
    • The main customer benefit
    • The next action visitors can take
    
    Keep the language natural, local and customer-focused.
    
    ────────────────────────
    ENGAGING SECTION HEADINGS
    ────────────────────────
    
    Create premium supporting headings from the available metafield content.
    
    Use heading patterns such as:
    
    Why Choose Our [Service Name] in [Suburb Name]
    
    How Our [Service Name] Works
    
    What Is Included With Your Service
    
    Professional Help for Large and Difficult Items
    
    Furniture Pickup and Delivery Across [Suburb Name]
    
    A Reliable Service for Marketplace and Store Purchases
    
    Areas We Serve Near [Suburb Name]
    
    Frequently Asked Questions About [Service Name]
    
    Book a [Service Name] in [Suburb Name]
    
    Use engaging, descriptive headings that clearly explain the following section.
    
    Maintain one H1 for the complete page.
    
    Use H2 for primary content sections.
    
    Use H3 for supporting topics within each H2 section.
    
    ────────────────────────
    CONTENT EXTENSION BLOCKS
    ────────────────────────
    
    Build the following dynamic content extensions whenever relevant metafield data is available:
    
    1. Service Summary
    
    Present a concise overview using the service name, suburb and service description.
    
    2. Key Service Benefits
    
    Display benefits as a responsive list or card grid.
    
    3. How the Service Works
    
    Create a numbered process using available process-step metafields.
    
    4. Items or Jobs Covered
    
    Display supported items, service types or customer situations.
    
    5. Local Service Coverage
    
    Present the primary suburb and nearby service areas naturally.
    
    6. Related Services
    
    Display crawlable internal links to relevant Shopify service pages.
    
    7. Customer Questions
    
    Present useful questions and answers from FAQ metafields.
    
    8. Conversion Section
    
    Display a clear call-to-action with quote and telephone buttons.
    
    Each extension should add useful information rather than repeat the same sentences from the page content.
    
